Mouka Ltd has unveiled a campaign tagged “Get the Mouka for You’’ to reward one consumer with a bedroom makeover worth one million naira.  The Head of Marketing, Mouka, Mrs Tolu Olanipekun, said this in a statement on Friday in Lagos. The statement said the campaign would encourage consumers to buy the right mattress based on their unique. It added that the campaign would educate consumers about the need to consider their age, body build, lifestyle and budget before choosing the right mattress. The statement noted that the campaign had been endorsed by the Nigeria Society of Physiotherapy and the National Association of Orthopaedic and Manual Therapists. It urged consumers to visit the company’s website for full details of the campaign. Mouka Ltd is fully committed to producing and delivering high quality brands of mattresses, other polyurethane products and accessories.